title: Healthy Miami Watch Face
summary: An open-source watch face that shows your Miami University spirit
description: Track your steps and show your Miami University spirit with this contemporary watch face.This app's use of the "Beveled M" logo has been officially approved by Miami University, but this app is not affiliated with or endorsed by Miami University.This project is free and open source. Source code can be obtained at https://github.com/brinkmwj/HealthyMiamiWatchFace
descriptionHTML:
Track your steps and show your Miami University spirit with this contemporary watch face.

This app's use of the "Beveled M" logo has been officially approved by Miami University, but this app is not affiliated with or endorsed by Miami University.

This project is free and open source. Source code can be obtained at https://github.com/brinkmwj/HealthyMiamiWatchFace
